metadata.name: Lonely Lake
metadata.description:
The piece is a reflection of infinite, limitless freedom
Separation from collectivity and acceptance of finitude ,the Piece registry is the desire to infinity.

In these photos maybe you can’t see the lost parts of my homeland (Iran ), also my world, Caspian sea, Gavazang Lake,
Urmia lake and Tehran or so many other views, so I captured a piece of them ,a piece of beauty ,a piece of limitless …….
